                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-268-off1369 t18170917-268-cd1370"></join>, one pair of sheets, value 1l.; three table-cloths, value 10s.; three towels, value 1s.; one shawl, value 5s.; two pillow-cases, value 2s.; one shift, value 1s.; one night-cap, value 3d., and one apron, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
